dmon\">Staedmon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Swann\" title=\"House Swann\">Swann</a><sup>1</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\">Tarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Whitehead\" title=\"House Whitehead\">Whitehead</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wylde\" title=\"House Wylde\">Wylde</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Knightly Houses</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-odd\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bolling\" title=\"House Bolling\">Bolling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Brownhill_(stormlands)\" title=\"House Brownhill (stormlands)\">Brownhill</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Connington\" title=\"House Connington\">Connington</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hasty\" title=\"House Hasty\">Hasty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Seaworth\" title=\"House Seaworth\">Seaworth</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Other Houses<br /><small>(noble rank unknown)</small></td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Gower\" title=\"House Gower\">Gower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Herston\" title=\"House Herston\">Herston</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Horpe\" title=\"House Horpe\">Horpe</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Kellington\" title=\"House Kellington\">Kellington</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Lonmouth\" title=\"House Lonmouth\">Lonmouth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Musgood\" title=\"House Musgood\">Musgood</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/H